Package buildingOrderModule.simulator

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ActionType
    ActionType.java --- The interface on which the Simulator performs its simulation.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActionSequence
    ActionSequence.java --- A sequence of ActionTypes that can / will be executed.
    ActionSequenceFactory
    ActionSequenceFactory.java --- A factory that stores and creates instances of ActionSequences.
    Node
    Node.java --- Class that is being used to represent a single Element in the tree that is being generated by the Simulator.
    NodeFactory
    NodeFactory.java --- A factory that stores and creates instances of Nodes.
    SimulationStarter
    SimulationStarter.java --- Class used for starting a simulation with the currently available and provided information.
    Simulator
    Simulator.java --- A Simulator for simulating the future possibilities of provided actions with a collection of available / free (Unit-) Types and busy / occupied ones.
    TypeWrapper
    TypeWrapper.java --- Wrapper Class for all types (UnitType, UpgradeType, etc.) for the different Races in the game.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    TypeWrapperException
    TypeWrapperException.java --- Exception for the TypeWrapper Class.
